"><small>GEE</small> Fe</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"17\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note17a\" data-full-marker=\"17a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124261136\" id=\"note17a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/25.19-24?lang=spa#p19\">Mos. 25:19–24</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"18\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note18a\" data-full-marker=\"18a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124261137\" id=\"note18a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.11?lang=spa#p11\">Mos. 1:11</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/5.8?lang=spa#p8\">5:8</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/jesus-christ?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Jesucristo — El tomar sobre sí el nombre de Jesucristo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"20\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note20a\" data-full-marker=\"20a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124261138\" id=\"note20a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/election?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Elección</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elect?lang=spa\">Elegidos</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/eternal-life?lang=spa\">Vida eterna</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"21\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note21a\" data-full-marker=\"21a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124261139\" id=\"note21a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/good-shepherd?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Buen Pastor</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"22\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note22a\" data-full-marker=\"22a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124261140\" id=\"note22a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.23?lang=spa#p23\">2 Ne. 9:23</a